## Letters

## Whitespace

Whitespace is implicitly present between all terms except for the ones
inside of a `no whitespace` box.

```=html
<svg class="railroad-diagram" viewBox="0 0 286 174">
<g transform="translate(.5 .5)">
<g>
<path d="M20 98v20m10 -20v20m-10 -10h20"></path>
